name: Pinky Totem
description:
800 x 800 | Digital drawing on Tayasui Sketch. 
A fun experiment using tools on the sketch app. Dia is exploring more shapes and concepts in her drawings and art. After a while, monsters and other imaginary friends are back in our daily life (i.e. there are currently three dragons in her room, sometimes there are monsters, etc).  
I am convincing myself that it's imaginary, because not sure how to handle it otherwise.
